 leechcraft-full
Provides:
 leechcraft-full
Description: modular live environment (full installation)
 This metapackage installs all main LeechCraft plugins.
 .
 LeechCraft is a free cross-platform modular live environment.
 .
 LeechCraft allows one to browse the web, chat using common IM networks, play
 music, read RSS/Atom feeds, download files via BitTorrent, read documents and
 much more.
 .
 LeechCraft is a modular system, and by installing different modules you can
 customize the feature set, keeping off the things you don't need and getting
 a decent IM client, media player or a feed reader, for example.

