Architecture: any
Depends:
 leechcraft-core (= ${binary:Version}),
 leechcraft-provider-html-wysiwyg,
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: blogging client for LeechCraft
 This package contains the base plugin of LeechCraft blogging client and its
 own sub-plugin:
  * metida (LiveJournal support)
  Supports all post fields available ranging from the post body itself to mood,
  location and avatar. It also supports fetching all the entries from a blog as
  well as local drafts and backups. LHTR module is used for editing, providing
  WYSIWYG functionality.
